Description: Comprehensive Git workflow management application for Linux
 A professional-grade, extensible Git desktop client with advanced workflow, visualization, and integration features.
 
 Features include:
  * Interactive visual Git graph with drag-and-drop operations
  * Advanced branch management and merge strategies
  * Git Flow and GitHub Flow support
  * Enhanced commit management with conventional commits
  * Multi-repository dashboard and analytics
  * Plugin system for extensibility
  * Security features including GPG signing and credential management
  * Modern themes and customizable interface
  * Performance optimization for large repositories 